    align:rationale "The AIDOC concept 'Data Training' is a general activity. The vair concept 'Unrepresentative Training Data' specifies *a type* of data training – specifically when the data used isn’t representative. Thus, unrepresentative training data is a specific case *of* data training."^^xsd:string ;
