    align:rationale "The AIDOC concept 'Data Training' is a general activity. 'Biased Training Data' (vair) describes a *specific type* of data training – one that contains bias. Therefore, biased training data is a narrower concept within the broader scope of data training."^^xsd:string ;
    align:relation skos:narrowMatch ;
    align:source aidoc:DataTraining ;
