    align:confidence "0.85"^^xsd:float ;
    align:rationale "Both concepts address human involvement in overseeing systems. The 'vair' concept explicitly mentions risk detection/prevention which adds a specific focus not directly stated in the AIDOC definition, but the core idea of facilitating human intervention is present in both. Therefore they are close matches rather than exact."^^xsd:string ;
    align:relation skos:closeMatch ;
    align:source aidoc:HumanOversightMechanism ;
